Articles.Content: I recently installed a mod but it requires a newer version of Modulemanager. my current version was already installed on another mod installation. I got a notification on the login screen that said "You have old versins of Module Manager (older than 2.0.10) or MMSarbianExt. You will need to remove them for Module Manager and the mods using it to work." Does anybody know where I can get a newer (preferably the newest) version of Module Manager?

Search this site

http://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/threads/55219-Module-Manager-2-1-5-%28May-22%29?highlight=module+manager

That should be it! Good luck
